OL,3,CWoman dies after car she was in
OL,4,Coverturns near Blyton
OL,6,FA 20-year-old woman has died after the
OL,7,Fcar she was in overturned near
OL,8,FGainsborough.
OL,10,FOfficers from Lincolnshire Police
OL,11,Fattended Bonsdale Lane in Blyton,
OL,12,Fafter a green Ford Fusion being driven
OL,13,Ftowards the junction with the B1205
OL,14,Foverturned Saturday, 7 March, near the
OL,15,Flevel crossing.
OL,17,FNo other vehicles were involved in the
OL,18,Fincident, which was reported to police
OL,19,Faround at 5.05pm.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
