PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773144740
OL,3,CWoman dies after car she was in
OL,4,Coverturns near Blyton
OL,6,FThe woman who was a passenger in the
OL,7,Fcar, was pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,9,FA 43-year-old man from the
OL,10,FGainsborough area was arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of death by dangerous
OL,12,Fdriving. He was also taken to hospital
OL,13,Fwith serious injuries.
OL,15,FLincolnshire Police said: "We are now
OL,16,Fappealing for anyone who saw the
OL,17,Fincident, has dashcam footage, or saw
OL,18,Fa green Ford Fusion in the area before
OL,19,Fthe collision to contact us."
